<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Live Tracker - Help Guide</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@300;400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="help-container">
        <h1>Welcome to Live Tracker!</h1>
        
        <section>
            <h2>Getting Started</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Click "Start Tracking" to begin sharing your location</li>
                <li>Toggle between km/mi units using the unit switch</li>
                <li>Switch between light/dark theme for comfort</li>
                <li>View connected users in real-time</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Map Features</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Switch between map styles using the dropdown</li>
                <li>Track your distance, duration, and speed</li>
                <li>View other users' locations in real-time</li>
                <li>Search for locations using the search bar</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Statistics</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Distance covered in km/miles</li>
                <li>Duration of your tracking session</li>
                <li>Average speed in km/h or mph</li>
                <li>Real-time updates as you move</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <a href="/" class="help-button">Back to Tracker</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>